12 An act relating to confirmatory adoptions
13 It is hereby enacted by the General Assembly of the State of Vermont:
14 Sec. 1. 15A V.S.A. § 1-114 is added to read:
15 § 1-114. CONFIRMATORY ADOPTION FOR CHILDREN BORN
16 THROUGH ASSISTED REPRODUCTION
17 (a) As used in this section:
18 (1) “Assisted reproduction” means a method of causing pregnancy other
19 than sexual intercourse and includes:
20 (A) intrauterine, intracervical, or vaginal insemination;
21 (B) donation of gametes;
